	<Title>
		Thyroid disease: Can it affect a person&apos;s mood?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Thyroid disease can affect mood, often causing anxiety or depression.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can thyroid disease affect my mood?
	</Question>
